  "text": "A recent report described patients with precocious pericardial effusion and later development of CAL [CITATION_1] . In our patients pericardial effusion was associated with coronaritis in 28 %, associated with aneurysms in 33%, and was documented earlier than coronary involvement, confirming previous findings.",
